Text:
Did you know that nearly 50% of employers that #outsource say the quality of their #service providers and a reactive versus proactive attitude is the most frustrating issues to deal with?

And how important the #team you are hiring is?

If you didn’t have to take the #PRICE under consideration when outsourcing a part of your work - who would you hire?

Don’t choose your outsourcing team based on their price (whether it’s a lower or a higher one - it doesn’t determine the quality of anyone’s work) choose it based on their experience.

Your #team should be:

1) Proactive;
2) Able to face the changes and challenges and adjust to them fast;
3) Reliable;
4) Experienced;
5) Willing to learn;
6) Ambitious;
7) Able to nurture your companies values just like it was their own;
8) Creative;
9) Able to act quickly!
10) RELIABLE!

Ask for a testimonial. Ask for proof that justifies the price. Talk to their previous clients. See if your energies align. Don't forget - the outsourcing team is there to take a part of the burden off your back, not the ones who will add to that cargo and make it even more difficult.

If you’re looking to outsource Lead Gen as part of your offering, if you would like to include it into your sales cycle or if you know anyone who is looking to outsource - DM me!
